### ⚙️ **Teknologi Disarankan**
| Mode | Framework | Database | UI/UX | Fitur Tambahan |
|------|------------|-----------|--------|----------------|
| **Desktop** | React + Chart.js/Recharts | Supabase | Tailwind / Chakra UI | Export CSV, fullscreen chart |
| **Mobile (PWA)** | React + Vite + Workbox | IndexedDB + Supabase Sync | Responsive grid | Offline caching, auto-sync |
| **Shared** | Supabase Auth + RLS | Multi-tenant schema | Bahasa Indonesia localization | Audit log + role-based access |

